<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT13">
<l>vīṭākkum peṟṟi yaṟiyātu meyvaruttik</l>
<l>kūṭākki niṉṟuṇṭu koṇṭuḻalvīr vīṭākku</l>
<l>meypporuḷtāṉ vēta mutaṟporuḷtāṉ viṇṇavarkku</l>
<l>naṟporuḷtā ṉārā yaṇaṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Not knowing the method that grants liberation, O you who wander around</l>
<l rend="indent">afflicting [your] bodies, making skeletons [of them],</l>
<l rend="indent">[by] standing [in penance] [and] eating [thereafter]!</l>
<l>Nārāyaṇa is the true Essence who grants liberation, the First Cause [as per] the Vedas</l>
<l>the good object [of enjoyment] for the celestials.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
